Package: rtrends
Type: Package
Title: Analyze Trends of R Packages Based on CRAN Logs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Avi Blinder  <aviblinder@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Avi Blinder <aviblinder@gmail.com>
Description: Analysis of CRAN logs in order to get daily historic data,
    for a specific package in a range of dates or data of several
    packages in a range of dates.
    The downloads logs are currently taken from <http://cran-logs.rstudio.com/>.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    lubridate,
    dplyr,
    tidyr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
